OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHill fog
OL,6,Fwill develop over the Pennines, with
OL,7,Fpatchy light rain likely at times.
OL,8,FElsewhere generally cloudy but staying
OL,9,Fmostly dry, although occasional light
OL,10,Frain may reach North Yorkshire.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloudy with hill fog across
OL,13,Fthe Pennines, patchy light rain easing
OL,14,Fbut showers developing later.
OL,15,FElsewhere mainly dry and cloudy, some
OL,16,Fbright spells developing. Feeling warm
OL,17,Fand humid. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
